		</div>
		<h2 class="dark:text-white text-lg py-2">Thank you for your purchase!</h2>
		<div class="w-80 text-center">
			<p class="py-2">You will receive a confirmation email with transaction details.</p>
			<br />
			<p>Once your tests are configured you will receive additional instructions for accessing your tests.</p>
		</div>
		<a 
			href="/CAT"
			class="mt-16 bg-green-700 rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-white w-80 shadow text-center text-lg border border-green-900 dark:border-slate-400"
		>
			Return to Test Ordering Homepage
